Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.11,Default CN,,0,0,0,,胡鬧怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:12.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:12.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,啊！
