Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,昂揚之勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:05.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,溢れる希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:05.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,滿溢之希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.20,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光り輝く絆とともに！
